                     <interp inst="t18320405-149-person1341" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner, and found in his right-hand trousers pocket this thimble and buckle.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. There was a dance at the house, and I found them in the passage.</p>
